Title: Miss March
Writer: Zach Cregger (screenplay), Trevor Moore (screenplay), Dennis Haggerty (story), Ryan Homchick (story), Thomas Mimms (story)
Actors: Zach Cregger, Trevor Moore, Raquel Alessi, Molly Stanton
Plot: Eugene believes in no sex before marriage. So DID his girlfriend, Cindi. His BFF loves sex. At Senior Prom, just before sex with Cindi, he falls into a coma. Waking up 4 years later, his Cindi is Miss March in Playboy. Can he get her back?
